I"E<p>The slider is considered one of the main parts in a classifieds site homepage, it attracts most of the usersâ€™ attention. Which is why we had a couple of options for you to choose from, each option shows different kind of ads at your homepage.</p>

<p><strong>You need to follow those steps:</strong></p>

<ol>
  <li>Log into your <strong>Admin Panel</strong></li>
  <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> &gt; <strong>Advertisement</strong></li>
  <li>At the <strong>Advertisements in home</strong> section choose one of the four available options.</li>
</ol>

<p><a href="//open-classifieds.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/How-to-manage-ads-in-slider1.png" class="thumbnail gallery-item" data-gallery="">
<img src="//open-classifieds.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/How-to-manage-ads-in-slider1.png" alt="How to manage ads in slider" />
</a></p>

<p><br />
The <strong>available options</strong> are:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Latest ads:</strong> It shows the last ads published at your website.</li>
  <li><strong>Featured ads:</strong> Displays ads that you chose to be featured.</li>
  <li><strong>Featured Ads Random:</strong> Displays ads which are featured in random order.</li>
  <li><strong>Popular Ads last month:</strong> Displays ads with most clicks/views during the past month.</li>
</ul>

